{"tid":1353843,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"細佬要考警察，唔識點同佢相處","createTime":"2019-07-23T04:39:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-14T02:57:19.000Z","uid":114217,"like":1,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"38ec6d299bdbdc8e37a6ae543ee1c1af27744c30","tid":1353843,"uid":114217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T04:39:57.000Z","msg":"細佬細我十年<br />\n由細睇到佢大<br />\n同佢感情亦都好好<br />\n會一齊睇戲睇波<br />\n<br />\n佢淺黃<br />\n今年考完DSE報咗紀律部隊課程<br />\n上年已經諗住考警察<br />\n咁警察薪高厚職，本身我都支持佢<br />\n<br />\n其實721前我對警察未算太反感<br />\n因為林鄭班狗官先係罪魁禍首<br />\n但721後已經完全仇警<br />\n<br />\n由尋日開始我已經好少同佢講野<br />\n今朝起身比咗張一早買咗嘅獅子王戲飛佢<br />\n同佢講呢套會係我地一齊睇嘅最後一套戲<br />\n佢話考到先算啦<br />\n<br />\n我好想說服自己佢依家都未考<br />\n到佢真係做咗黑警先各行各路都唔遲<br />\n依家暫時當乜野都無發生先<br />\n<br />\n但我真係呃唔到自先做唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f5402520f029e68b3d241f436f0e36a22e0fc07","tid":1353843,"uid":23815,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T04:43:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有得揀都唔揀<br />\n條路自己揀 仆街唔好喊"},{"pid":"43871c370d31734bf1fe2d2234fdd648ab3e8ec9","tid":1353843,"uid":39796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T04:45:28.000Z","msg":"唔識考海關消防咩"},{"pid":"8139b7ef6ce12728cad8a4ee4bd2f7cbd5076129","tid":1353843,"uid":34415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T04:46:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/520eo1h.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F520eo1h.jpg&h=32ecfa79&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SMbASUF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSMbASUF.jpg&h=a2ce6deb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kjPbreK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkjPbreK.jpg&h=068b8664&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tKrX6eR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtKrX6eR.jpg&h=922f47ab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/87OcaGA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F87OcaGA.jpg&h=5d1b1e66&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3980e69e5d31dfa9b1f8f82610fd83291e59f2f8","tid":1353843,"uid":114217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"43871c370d31734bf1fe2d2234fdd648ab3e8ec9","tid":1353843,"uid":39796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T04:45:28.000Z","msg":"唔識考海關消防咩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T04:52:28.000Z","msg":"警察相對上易考d<br />\n兼且人工高d"},{"pid":"590601a0b9a0a0c054dc0cb395b04f9fd7bc4f95","tid":1353843,"uid":214192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T04:54:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>由尋日開始我已經好少同佢講野<br />\n今朝起身比咗張一早買咗嘅獅子王戲飛佢<br />\n同佢講呢套會係我地一齊睇嘅最後一套戲<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">佢話考到先算啦</span></blockquote><br />\n如果佢講得出呢句佢自己都心存芥蒂，對於警察都有啲抵觸<br />\n你地感情好嘅話拉佢入房慢慢心平氣和咁傾，流露曬自己啲真性情出嚟試下勸佢唔好考"},{"pid":"4bb04bea7f0f8d45d5dfbc6811faf262d37526e8","tid":1353843,"uid":165783,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T04:56:44.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">其實721前我對警察未算太反感</span></span><br />\n<br />\n你都唔係好你細佬好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n按你道理班狗繼續周街咬人 元朗再冇人劈友嘅話 你都可以支持細佬做狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4178d0e1911e855306e57daa3facb555f185d92","tid":1353843,"uid":89337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T05:06:43.000Z","msg":"佢<span style=\"color: red;\">淺黃</span><br />\n今年考完DSE報咗紀律部隊課程<br />\n上年已經諗住考警察<br />\n<br />\n淺黃仲諗住做警犬 咪扮曬野啦<br />\n<br />\n咁警察<span style=\"color: red;\">薪高厚職</span>，本身我都支持佢<br />\n<br />\n所以而家仲想做警犬都係因為份糧 唔好同我講佢會做好警察之類既廢話 咁既事勢仲為左份糧根本就係埋沒良心"},{"pid":"cd7bf7a0033b0401ba96779542ac5c1867bb505d","tid":1353843,"uid":7855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T02:57:19.000Z","msg":"仲有得教 <br />\n教返好佢啦"}]}